i\';&quot;&gt;围绕大橘子成长或者以商品交易为中心，展开联想与思索，给出1-9级的头衔名。给我们大橘子网站冠名。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;三、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;征集方式&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Microsoft YaHei;&quot;&gt;请各位贤人志士将自己的想法与等级头衔称谓发往我们的官方邮箱：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:hi@bigoranger.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#E56600;&quot;&gt;hi@bigoranger.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;四、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;征集时间&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Microsoft YaHei;&quot;&gt;2014&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;日起，至&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span styl