ly:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Microsoft YaHei;&quot;&gt;大师奖：￥&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;200&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;七、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;评选细则&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;本次征集活动的原则是公正、公开、公平&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;每一位参赛者有且只有一个参赛作品&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;作品要求：等级必须包含9个等级以上；规范按照：【等级】【对应的等级称号】，例如【Lv 1】【幼儿园】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';&quot;&gt;4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span sty